Package: apsimx
Title: Inspect, Read, Edit and Run APSIM-X "Next Generation" and APSIM "Classic"
Version: 1.921
Authors@R: person("Fernando", "Miguez", email = "femiguez@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4627-8329"))
Description: The functions in this package inspect, read, edit and run .apsimx (JSON) and .apsim (XML)
             files and run them from within R through the command line. The .apsim files correspond to
	     APSIM "Classic" (7.x) - Windows only - and the .apsimx files correspond to APSIM-X "Next Generation".
	     For more information about APSIM see (www.apsim.info) and for APSIM
	     next generation (https://apsimnextgeneration.netlify.com/). 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
